---
title: Honey-Garlic Chicken Thigh Wraps with Potato Wedges and Ranch
description: This is pub food at its finest, made in the comfort of your own home! And what better way to get some extra veggies into dinner than by putting them in a wrap bursting with classic honey-garlic flavour?! These wraps are sure to be a hit with the whole family.
